📊 CHANNEL IDENTITY & POSITIONING

Mission Statement

You\'re a public historian showing why historical accuracy matters.
Oversimplification and romanticization can be dangerous---your role is
revealing how distorted history fuels present-day conflicts and
misconceptions.

Core Value Proposition

**\"History vs Hype\"** - Clear branding that signals myth-busting with
evidence

What Your Audience Expects

-   Rigorous fact-checking with transparent methodology

-   Primary sources and academic citations

-   Nuanced analysis (not binary good/evil narratives)

-   Acknowledgment of complexity and counter-evidence

-   Myth-busting backed by evidence, not opinion

